description: AMUNDI S&P GLOBAL LUXURY UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the evolution of the S&P Global Luxury, net return index, denominated in USD, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to major luxury-related securities in the world, in a single transaction. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi S&P Global Luxury UCITS ETF - USD (C)
